Package eu.europa.ec.eurostat.grid.examples

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EurostatDataPreparation  
    EurostatGridsProduction
    Examples to produce European grids based on ETRS89-LAEA coordinate reference system (EPSG:3035) for various resolutions.
    EurostatLandProportionComputation  
    EurostatPopulationGridMultiResolution
    Derive EU population figures from 1km grid to other larger resolutions.
    StatGridCountryUtil
    A number of functions to assign country codes to grid cells.
